@development

### Registrar Usuario
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombreUsuario": "elias_test11",
  "email": "elias@test11.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Generar Secreto 2FA
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/2fa-secret?username=elias_test11 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombreUsuario": "elias_test10",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login con 2FA (Obtener JWT y guardarlo)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login-2fa HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombreUsuario": "elias_test11",
  "token2FA": "152742"
}

